commit.message: Update README to add a link to the Guix package.
Fix link number for emacs-ansilove in the "Projects using Ansilove" section.
Add a link to Durdraw in the "Projects using Ansilove" section.
Bump copyright year to 2024.
Release ansilove 4.2.0.
Update ChangeLog.
Add support for the Spleen 8x16 font. Requires libansilove >= 1.4.0.
Add initial RPM spec file.
Add a link to emacs-ansilove in the "Projects using Ansilove" section.
Release ansilove 4.1.7.
Update ChangeLog.
Fix AnsiLove 4.1.6 release date, it was released in 2022, not 2021.
Harmonize the line on packages availability accross all projects.
Add link to Homebrew package in the README.
Move manual page to the man directory.
Bump copyright year to 2023.
Point the OpenBSD package link to openports.pl.
Always print processing time on stderr.
Bump copyright year to 2022 in seccomp.h.
List projects using Ansilove in the README.
Add a link to the Gentoo package in the README.
Release ansilove 4.1.6.
Update ChangeLog.
Stop linking against libm, it's not necessary anymore.
Bump copyright year to 2022.
Add a link to the Monochrome Display Adapter notes from John Elliott.
Use CMAKE_C_STANDARD instead of hardcoding compiler flags.
